# Never bake secret env files into the image — env_file in docker-compose
# is the single source of truth at runtime. Without this, a stray .env in
# the build context (e.g. a developer's local file) gets COPYed into /app
# and silently shadows the env_file values via Next.js dotenv auto-loading.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
!.env.example
